              "key": "name",
              "value": "laptop",
              "description": "Keyword to search for, case-insensitive partial match against category name"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Search categories by name (case-insensitive, partial match).\n\nAny authenticated user (Employee or Admin) can call this.\n\nExpected Response: Array of matching CategoryRespDto\n[\n  { \"id\": 1, \"categoryName\": \"Laptops\", \"description\": \"All Laptop computers\" }\n]"
      }
